{
  "title": "Buttery Silky Saudian Cream Stir-fry",
  "description": "A decadent and creamy dish perfect for post-workout recovery, featuring a rich blend of dairy products that provide essential nutrients to help rebuild muscle tissue.",
  "cuisine": "Saudi Arabian",
  "diet": [
